      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches, scuffs, and areas of paint wear beyond normal use, though there are no major structural dents. The interior has visible wear including faded upholstery and minor surface damage. Mechanically, the car runs but may have minor issues that should be inspected before purchase.",
